| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                     |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: c DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=10                                                                                                                                       |
|               |   Projection: hits.SearchPhrase, min(hits.URL), count(*) AS c                                                                                                            |
