| physical_plan | SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[c@2 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[false]                                                                                                 |
|               |   CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[SearchPhrase@0 as SearchPhrase, min(hits.URL)@1 as min(hits.URL), count(*)@2 as c]                                                             |
|               |       AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[SearchPhrase@0 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[min(hits.URL), count(*)]                                                         |
|               |         CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                      |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([SearchPhrase@0], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                  |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[SearchPhrase@1 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[min(hits.URL), count(*)]                                                            |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                 CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                              |
|               |                   FilterExec: CAST(URL@0 AS LargeUtf8) LIKE %google% AND SearchPhrase@1 !=                                                                               |
|               |                     SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                                              |
|               |                         FallbackOnZeroResultsScanExec                                                                                                                    |
|               |                           CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                         |
|               |                             RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                                        |
|               |                               DuckSqlExec sql=                                                                                                                           |
